flavor_text: It fights by swinging a piece of lumber around. It is close to evolving when it can handle the lumber without difficulty.
These Pokemon appear at building sites and help out with construction. They always carry squared logs.
Always carrying squared logs they help out with construction. As they grow they carry bigger logs.
